  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the broiler to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the yogurt, garlic, ginger, cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the mushrooms to the bowl and toss to coat with the yogurt mixture.",
    "Thread the mushrooms onto skewers, leaving a small space between each mushroom.",
    "Brush the mushrooms with olive oil and place the skewers on a broiler pan.",
    "Broil the mushrooms for 10-12 minutes, or until they are tender and lightly browned.",
    "Serve the mushrooms hot, garnished with fresh parsley or cilantro.",
    "Offer a side of pita bread or rice to mop up the creamy sauce.",
    "Garnish with lemon wedges and serve immediately."
  ],
